<p>XIV. Ver&ugrave;m vbi conce$$um fuerit corpu$cula
qu&aelig;dam ex magnete procedere, qu&aelig; ferrum ad ip-
$um pelliciant; intelligi-ne tamen pote$t, aut qua
form&acirc; $int, vt attractionis organa fiant; aut quomo-
