ex$ilientia tant&ograve; rariora fiant, quant&ograve; procedunt
<pb n=59>
longi&ugrave;s, $icque min&ugrave;s conferta min&ugrave;s polleant, &amp;
$uperat&acirc; quadam di$tanti&acirc;, attractioni imparia, ac
