in ip$o Terra, an lapis $tatim h&ucirc;c contendet? Si fieri
dicas, oportet $an&egrave; $entiri Terram &agrave; lapide, deber&eacute;-
que proinde Terram tran$mittere in ip$um vim
quandam, atque ade&ograve; corpu$cula, quibus $ui $en$um
